  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The witch can cause doubt to creep into the mind of a foe within 30 feet that she can see. The target takes a &ndash;2 penalty on one of the following (witch's choice): AC, ability checks, attack rolls, saving throws, or skill checks. This hex lasts for a number of rounds equal to 3 + the witch's Intelligence modifier. A Will save reduces this to just 1 round. This is a mind-affecting effect.</p>\n<p>At 8th level the penalty increases to &ndash;4.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Usage</strong></p>\n<p>Set the item level to the Level of the Witch (Up to level 8) using the ability.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
